summary: Land created specialy for Tundra Defence
descriptionHtml:
Land specialy for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22330/]Tundra Defense[/url]. Can accommodate a large city.
Contains a flat surface with navmeshed roads.
Transport accessibility from docks of Solitude and Dawnstar, just search a ships.

==============================================
[i]About world`s name.
[img]http://buhalo.org/pictures/tarif_ked_korolevstvo.jpg[/img]
In 1989, in Soviet Union, was recorded famous prank calls with «Grandfather of Information Technology Centre» (Ded IVC) victim. In conversation, he often mentioned «Kedovskoe damned kingdom»(«Kedovskoe korolevstvo prokljatoe»), which would destroy the unguided rockets. The name «Kedovskoe» comes from the word «sneakers» («kedy»), who at that time often wore a Soviet youth. The mod is dedicated to this phrase, also, they contain anti-missile hideout. Full transcript of the conversation at [url=http://buhalo.org/text.htm]http://buhalo.org/text.htm[/url][/i]
